, {\"sentence\": \"ET in the 2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 385, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can watch the meet for free with trials fromFuboorDIRECTV Stream, and it will also be available onSlingandPeacock.\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The first of these three can be set to record the meet ahead of time if you do not plan to watch live.\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 609, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peacock will automatically upload events as they are completed to watch later.\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NBC will also air clips from the meet as part of their Primetime coverage Thursday night at 8 p.m.\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 787, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 689, \"end\": 692, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9875861645497693, \"rank\": 0.007926964260395786, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ET.\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 791, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Each country sends their top two athletes from the qualification meet to the all-round meet.\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 885, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the United States, it was a close competition on who the second representative would be as Sunisa Lee and Jordan Chiles both put up a good fight.\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 1035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 894, \"end\": 907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.6110722413076344, \"rank\": 0.635413202278181, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 981, \"end\": 991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sunisa Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\",